masa_gadget_mod.config.generic.openConfi: A hotkey to open the in-game Config GUI
masa_gadget_mod.config.generic.searchMob: Search mob spawn point. Need set §6Despawn Sphere§r in minihud, and light check depends on §6lightLevelThreshold§r in minihud
masa_gadget_mod.config.generic.syncAllEn: Use pcaSyncProtocol to sync all entity data.
masa_gadget_mod.config.litematica.better: Easy place mode can open inventory (such as chest, hopper, etc.), and can use beacon.
masa_gadget_mod.config.litematica.disabl: Disable easyPlace failure that annoying prompt window.
masa_gadget_mod.config.litematica.saveIn: Use pcaSyncProtocol to sync inventory data to local and save to schematic
masa_gadget_mod.config.litematica.useRel: Save and load schematic use relative path
masa_gadget_mod.config.malilib.fastSwitc: Render drop down list widget, player can switch other masa's mod config gui quickly.
masa_gadget_mod.config.malilib.fixConfig: Use the length of getTranslatedGuiDisplayName as widget width
masa_gadget_mod.config.malilib.optimizeC: Make search support uppercase, translate text, and can use §6modified§r to search modified config
masa_gadget_mod.config.minihud.compactBb: Parse bbor protocol and send data to minihud
masa_gadget_mod.config.minihud.pcaSyncPr: Press §6inventoryPreview§r hotkey to use PCA sync protocol to sync Beehive
masa_gadget_mod.config.tweakeroo.autoSyn: Auto sync the trade offer list of villager
masa_gadget_mod.config.tweakeroo.invento: Inventory preview will render the output of comparator.
Inventory preview support largeBarrel (need tis carpet).
Player can use inventory preview on free camera
Player can use inventory preview to show the inventory of player and ender chest inventory

When player press the inventory preview hotkey, player can use the mouse wheel to select items (player can view the enchantment information), and when player select the shulker box in the chest, player can press the mouse scroll to preview the items in the box
Inventory preview support shulker box item entity.
Inventory preview will preview the trade offer list of merchant
masa_gadget_mod.config.tweakeroo.pcaSync: Use pcaSyncProtocol to sync block entity data and entity data from server, such as chest, villager
masa_gadget_mod.config.tweakeroo.renderN: Render next restock time on villager.
masa_gadget_mod.config.tweakeroo.renderT: Render trade enchanted book text on villager.
masa_gadget_mod.config.tweakeroo.renderZ: Render zombie villager convert time on zombie villager.
